name: Live Note
description: Live note is a mobile centered progressive web app. I build it for better note taking during meetings and classes. This app consists of starting an audio note, and as it records the user can add timestamped comments and picture to the note. This gives note taking: audio, visual and textual context for a more detailed note.

name: Fanshawe Intramurals

name: Complaints Check
description: A web app where property manager can track tenants complaints and keep records of them It integrates a CMS to manage complaints and a client-side interface where tenants can log in and place complaints with photo evidence and detailed description's.
